<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10559538>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Hemisphaerius bresseeli sp. nov., paratype, ♀ from Vietnam, Dong Son-Ky Thuong Nature Reserve (RBINS). A. Habitus, dorsal view.B. Habitus, ventral view.C. Habitus, lateral view.D. Habitus, perpendicular view of frons." ;
