<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10559542>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Hemisphaerius bresseeli sp. nov., paratypes, specimens identified as H. bipunctatus Melichar, 1906 from Hoa Binh (RBINS). A–D. Male. A. Dorsal view. B. Lateral view. C. Frontal view. D. Labels. E–H. Female. E. Dorsal view. F. Lateral view. G. Frontal view. H. Labels." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10559542/files/figure.png" ;
