<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10559544>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Hemisphaerius bresseeli sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (RBINS), terminalia. A–D. Pygofer, anal tube and gonostyli. A. Lateral view. B. Laterocaudal view. C. Caudal view. D. Dorsal view. E–K. Aedeagus and connective. E. Left lateral view. F. Right lateral view. G. Caudal view. H. Ventral view. I. Dorsal view. J. Anterodorsal view. K. Laterocaudal view, perpendicular to plane of posterolateral lobes of periandrium. Abbreviations: see Material and methods." ;
